channel.title: RsInBlack- We begin where Runescape ended
channel.description:
First of all, Rate the title ^^:):D [b]317 gameframe. 100% autocast 100% ring/necklace teleporting 100% rushing 100% specials 80% dueling, sometimes it bugs. Perfect Timers! Lots of working skills! 99% clan chat! 2 working quests! soon to come more! [/b]
Some help in the development team would be nice!
Source coder: 1.Rene(me) 2. Open.
Client coder: 1.open 2.open
If you would like to code, Please use this form.
Do you have experience, if so which? Your name: no i don't mean names like nookumpuck i mean like Your name. lol. Is my server smexi so far? Do you like waffles?
Kk now for some pics [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/dds-snpNI.png[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/cc-Lf7u3.png[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/1-SEMOo.png[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/2-JViyW.png[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/3-sGwiF.png[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/4-4lD1p.png[/img]
Ill post more in a few hours, gotta go now. If you would like to check it out, you can download the client from rsinblack.org/client.rar Note: this is not considered as advertising i hope? o.O
